title: DGBRSM Truck Tool Box Lock with 2 Keys Compatible with Uws Dee Zee Delta Kobalt Better Built Husky Craftsman Toolbox
features: PREMIUM MATERIAL: Made of zinc alloy, rust-proof and durable.

Separate Keys: The cam lock can only be unlocked with the two keys provided to protect the security and privacy of your important special items. The key adopts a non-fixed design and can be taken out to unlock or close the door.

Product Design: The truck toolbox lock adopts a closed groove design, which can effectively prevent sand and dust. The lock plate adopts a riveted design, which is more firm, shock-resistant, and prevents the lock core screw from falling off.
Product Compatibility: 16mm Truck Tool Cylinder, 22mm Bolt Length, for Universal Handle Paddle Locks, Compatible with UWS, Dee Zee, Delta, Kobalt, Better Built, Husky, Craftsman and Weatherguard.
Package Contains: 1 Piece - Truck Toolbox Lock Compatible with Uws Dee Zee Delta Kobalt Better Build Husky Craftsman.
